OL,3,CCouncil facing hundreds of legal
OL,4,Cclaims from workers at centre of bin
OL,5,Cstrikes
OL,7,FBirmingham City Council is facing more
OL,8,Fthan 400 legal claims from bin workers
OL,9,Fwhose pay has been unfairly attacked -
OL,10,Fthat's according to the union at the
OL,11,Fcentre of the long-running Birmingham
OL,12,Fbin strike.
OL,14,FWorkers, supported by Unite, started
OL,15,Ftaking industrial action more than a
OL,16,Fyear ago and have been on all-out
OL,17,Fstrike since last March over claims
OL,18,Fthat planned reforms to the council's
OL,19,Frefuse collection service would lead
OL,20,Fto pay cuts of thousands of pounds.
