OL,7,FThe total liability for the claims
OL,8,Fwould be several million pounds,
OL,9,Fhigher than outlined in a deal agreed
OL,10,Fwith the conciliation service, Acas,
OL,11,Fin May, said Unite.
OL,13,FIf the strike is not resolved before
OL,14,FMay, whichever party wins control of
OL,15,Fthe council after the election will
OL,16,Fhave to pick up the bill, said Unite.
OL,18,FGeneral secretary Sharon Graham said:
OL,19,F"Unite will use every tool available
OL,20,Fto defend and protect its members and
OL,21,Fthat includes legal action.
