OL,7,F"Unite's message to Birmingham council
OL,8,Fis clear ` it needs to return to
OL,9,Fnegotiations and offer a fair deal to
OL,10,Fits workers. Every day this dispute
OL,11,Fcontinues is seeing the council's
OL,12,Fcosts climb ever further.
OL,14,F"This dispute will not end until there
OL,15,Fis justice for bin workers."
OL,17,FA council spokesperson said the
OL,18,Fauthority has received a number of
OL,19,Flegal claims from Unite, which the
OL,20,Fcouncil intends to contest.
