OL,7,FThe spokesperson said: "The council
OL,8,Fhas engaged in negotiations with
OL,9,FUnite, but they have rejected our fair
OL,10,Fand reasonable offers.
OL,12,F"Unite's demands would leave us with
OL,13,Fanother equal pay bill of hundreds of
OL,14,Fmillions of pounds, which is totally
OL,15,Funacceptable, and would jeopardise the
OL,16,Fconsiderable progress we have made in
OL,17,Four financial recovery."
