OL,7,FThe council said all of the 170 staff
OL,8,Faffected by the reforms to the service
OL,9,Fwere redeployed or elected to take
OL,10,Fvoluntary redundancy.
OL,12,FThe spokesperson said: "Given this, it
OL,13,Fis hard to understand why the strike
OL,14,Fis continuing.
OL,16,F"We have invited Unite on multiple
OL,17,Foccasions to make a proposal to end
OL,18,Fthe strike, which we would fully and
OL,19,Fcarefully consider, but they have
OL,20,Fdeclined to do so thus far."
